===Noun===
'''bhikkhu''' (''plural'' '''bhikkhus''')
#A Buddhist [[monk]] or [[priest]]; one who follows all Buddhist precepts as a full member of the [[sangha]].

====Etymology====
From the [[Pali]], meaning a "beggar."

